Package Inheritance

Class Waterfowl

java.lang.Object
Inheritance.Bird
Inheritance.Waterfowl
Direct Known Subclasses:
Duck
public class Waterfowl extends Bird
The Waterfowl class is a subclass of Bird. This class is intended to be extended by more specific waterfowl types, such as ducks.
